values:
Gawd...Once again I return to a home that looks like a bomb went off.
My husbond has once again not lifted a finger to clear up the mess, I just don't get it,
Are they simply borned without conscience, or is it just the Y kromosone that's allowing them to block it out? AAARGH, I'm no fucking maid!!!!! (sorry, I just had to get that out of my system).
I don't get it... Noone seems to have heard anything about the 2007 tour, since Gert let a rumour slip months ago... I think he pulled a "Landers" on us...grrrrr
Gaaaah...Im never eating junkfood again...I'm so sick...
UUUUUH, I've just heard the rumour about a huge Rammstein tour 2007....Drool...oh eeew, drool on my new sweater...whine...

Oh YES!!!!!!

I got a job a job dum da dum a joooooooob!!!!

YAY, WOOOT, TA-DAAAAAM!

gasp...gotta get of the damn sugar...gasp...pant...
wooow for Rammstein, woooohooo for a hot indian summer, woohooo for LJ, Wooohooo for me....gasp....no more sugar...never again...gasp gasp
26 years old...damn how did I get this old?????
